name: :spasm:
description: Everyone's favourite emoji in r/phigrosGame Discord server. The character which this emoji features is Kuzumi. She is one of the characters from Phigros, a rhythm game made by Pigeon Games. Kuzumi makes an appearance in an illustration for a song named "Spasmodic" (where name for emoji "spasm" comes from) and also plays a relatively big part in Phigros story.
